				<div class="newsD-article-title">
					<h2>后勤零星维修公司遴选(第二次)采购项目磋商结果公告</h2>
					<p style="font-size:14px;">汉中市第一医院（汉中市妇女儿童医院）官网&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-size:14px;">2024-07-11 16:39:27</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;来源：&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;阅读量：7779</p>
				</div>
				<div class="newsD-article-content">
					<p>
						<p style="text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:方正小标宋简体;font-size:29px"><span style="font-family:方正小标宋简体">汉中市铁路中心医院后勤零星维修公司遴选</span><span style="font-family:方正小标宋简体">(第二次)采购项目</span></span><span style=";font-family:方正小标宋简体;font-size:29px">磋商结果公告</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">汉中市铁路中心医院后勤零星维修公司遴选</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">(第二次)采购项目</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">评审工作已完毕，</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">现将</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">评审结果公示如下：</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">一、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">项目名称：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">后勤零星维修公司遴选</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">(第二次)采购项目</span></span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">二、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">磋商结果</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">：</span></p><table><tbody><tr style="height:37px" class="firstRow"><td width="264" valign="top" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-color: windowtext;"><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">项目名称</span></p></td><td width="264" valign="top" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-color: windowtext;"><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px">中标单位</span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:37px"><td width="264" valign="center" rowspan="3" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;"><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">后勤零星维修公司遴选</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">(第二次)采购项目</span></span></p></td><td width="264" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;"><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:16px">陕西外经贸城乡建设集团有限公司</span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:37px"><td width="264" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;"><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:16px">陕西东元汉升建设有限公司</span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:38px"><td width="264" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;"><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:16px">汉中市创景建设有限公司</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">三、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">评委成员名单：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">杨卫强</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">王宁</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:仿宋">冯耀耀</span> <span style="font-family:仿宋">甘小娣</span> <span style="font-family:仿宋">李文婷</span> </span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">四、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">本公告公示期</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">1</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">天，投标供应商如对此公告有异议的，请于此公告发布之日起</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">七</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">个工作日内，以书面形式向采购人提出质疑。</span></p><p style="text-indent:64px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">采购人：汉中市铁路中心医院</span></p><p style="text-indent:64px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">地址：汉中市汉台区石马路中段</span></p><p style="text-indent:64px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">联系人：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">黄先生</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">佘先生</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:64px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">联系电话：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">0916-2245163</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:64px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">监督投诉电话：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">0916-</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">2692140</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:64px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px; text-align: center;">汉中市铁路中心医院</span></p><p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px; text-align: center;">2024年7月11日&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>					</p>
					<!--<a href="#">返回</a>-->
				</div>
